ylva
------------------------------------------
Password management belongs to the command line, deep into the Unix heartland,
the shell.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libqrcodegen1-1.8.0-1bl1
  libsqlite3_0-3.49.1-1
  libssl3-3.5.6-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libqrcodegen-devel-1.8.0-1bl1
  libsqlite3-devel-3.49.1-1
  libssl-devel-3.5.6-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/nrosvall/ylva

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/nrosvall/ylva/archive/refs/tags/v1.7.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ylva-1.7-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ylva-1.7-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ylva-1.7-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ylva-1.7-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(ylva)
  /usr/bin/ylva.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ylva.README
  /usr/share/doc/ylva/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/ylva/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/ylva/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/ylva/ylva.png
  /usr/share/man/man1/ylva.1.gz

